屠苏。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7e1b62222e"},{"id":"56d74c1433","type":"paragraph","text":"千门万户瞳瞳日，总把新桃换旧符。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7e1b62222e"},{"id":"a4b3552aee","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七六年二月三日有感。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7e1b62222e"},{"id":"cf1370dac2","type":"paragraph","text":"张春桥引用的一首诗的出处和注释（抄自《千家诗》一九五七年版）","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7e1b62222e"},{"id":"128d8bab6e","type":"paragraph","text":"元  日      （王安石）","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7e1b62222e"},{"id":"d53afa58ca","type":"paragraph","text":"爆竹声中一岁除，春风送暖入屠苏。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7e1b62222e"},{"id":"d6b4ea1bfd","type":"paragraph","text":"千门万户瞳瞳日，总把新桃换旧符。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7e1b62222e"},{"id":"8db2726454","type":"paragraph","text":"爆竹、山家以除夕烧竹、竹爆裂之声、山魈闻声畏惧而远避。屠苏、美酒名。瞳瞳、日初出貌。桃符、以桃木刻符于门、以御鬼也。岁去春来、春风吹暖、以助酒力醺也。一岁之始、家家换隙桃符、以贺新正。此诗自况其初拜相时、得君行政、除旧布新、而始行已之政令也。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7e1b62222e"}],"page":{"id":"963855f48e","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7e1b62222e","start":0,"end":0}},"zhangchunqiao":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"00a5af8c92","type":"paragraph","text":"爆竹、山家以除夕烧竹、竹爆裂之声、山魈闻声畏惧而远避。屠苏、美酒名。瞳瞳、日初出貌。桃符、以桃木刻符于门、以御鬼也。岁去春来、春风吹暖、以助酒力醺也。一岁之始、家家换隙桃符、以贺新正。此诗自况其初拜相时、得君行政、除旧布新、而始行已之政令也。","index":14,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7e1b62222e"},{"id":"026e6551ac","type":"title","text":"张春桥日记","index":0,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7e1b62222e"},{"id":"0bb72a76ed","type":"paragraph","text":"爆竹声中一岁除，东风送暖入屠苏。","index":7,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7e1b62222e"},{"id":"0daaf5ff2c","type":"paragraph","text":"又是一个一号文件。","index":1,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7e1b62222e"},{"id":"12cef5ae3b","type":"paragraph","text":"元日（王安石）","index":11,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7e1b62222e"},{"id":"302edff237","type":"paragraph","text":"来得快，来得凶，垮得也快。","index":3,"